Oracle-CAPI version 0.01
=================

A perl XS wrapper to ctapi.h from the Oracle Collaboration Suite CAPI SDK (CSDK). This was built and
tested against OCS version 9.0.4.2 on Linux.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

Make sure the Oracle CAPI SDK (CSDK) lib is visible (ln -s .../where_CAPI/lib lib - try $ORACLE_HOME/ocal/sdk/lib)

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Oracle CAPI SDK c lib (CSDK):
-lcapi -lclntsh -lctcore

